headline: Palo Alto (PANW) Gets Downgraded, Flutter (FLUT) Cuts Its Guidance
summary: Deutsche Bank lowered its rating today on Palo Alto Networks (PANW), one of investors’ favorite names in the IT security sector, while FanDuel owner Flutter (FLUT) cut its guidance, Schwab TV reported today. Deutsche Bank cut its rating on PANW to Hold from Buy. Additionally, Deutsche reduced its price target on the shares to $190 […]
